channel.title: How would I change my client's Icon?
channel.description: [center]Hello Moparscape, I'm wondering how I can change my client's Icon on my R.S.P.S ( Runescape private server ) The revision is a 317 Project insanity base if that matters any? I already have the icon to change it, But I don't know how to change it? Can someone make a tutorial or something on helping me change the picture of the client's icon, I bet a lot of people been asking the same question so it will help a lot of people! Thanks[/center]
